nformation very quickly. and i don\'t have to checking do many searching data. so i don\'t waste my time.','2026-03-27 16:20:07'),(33,1,1086,'FREE',1,'/uploads/audio/user1_part3_q0_20260327_162005.webm',NULL,NULL,'2026-03-27 16:20:38'),(34,1,1088,'FREE',1,NULL,'[{\"question\":\"Do you currently use any AI-powered tools or features in your daily life, such as virtual assistants or personalized recommendations? If so, what are some examples?\",\"answer\":\"yes, I used to AI applications in my daily life. so I can get many information anytime anywhere.\"},{\"question\":\"How often do you rely on these AI tools, and in what ways do you find them most helpful for your daily routine?\",\"answer\":\"yes, using AI tools with daily work is the biggest benefit. because I don\'t waste time using AI tools.\"},{\"question\":\"Looking ahead, what do you think will be the most significant positive or negative impact of AI on people\'s daily lives in the next five to ten years? Explain your reasoning.\",\"answer\":\"Some people believe AI will significantly improve our quality of life in the future, while others are concerned about its potential risks. What is your overall opinion on the future impact of AI, and why?\"}]',NULL,'2026-03-27 16:22:42'),(35,1,1094,'FREE',1,NULL,'[{\"question\":\"Do you currently use any AI-powered tools or applications in your daily life? If so, could you give an example of one you find useful?\",\"answer\":\"yes, I used to AI applications in my daily life. so I can get many information anytime anywhere.\"},{\"question\":\"In your opinion, what is the biggest advantage of integrating AI technology into our everyday tasks and routines?\",\"answer\":\"yes, using AI tools with daily work is the biggest benefit. because I don\'t waste time using AI tools.\"},{\"question\":\"Looking ahead, how do you foresee AI continuing to impact our personal and professional lives in the next five to ten years? Give specific reasons to support your view.\",\"answer\":\"Some people believe AI will significantly improve our quality of life in the future, while others are concerned about its potential risks. What is your overall opinion on the future impact of AI, and why?\"}]',NULL,'2026-03-27 16:49:26'),(36,1,1101,'FREE',1,NULL,NULL,'yes, i agree experimenting with a four-day work week. let me explain what i think so. most of all experimenting with a five-day work week is making employee so tired. for example, when i was a employee. i was tired every day, so i wasn\'t able to focus on my work. but, when i was experimenting with a four-day work week, i was able to focus my work. also compaire to past, senior like my fathers age was experimenting with a six-day work week. but it\'s make it same performances when they worked fie days. ','2026-03-27 17:16:41'),(37,1,1104,'FREE',1,NULL,NULL,'yes, i agree experimenting with a four-day work week. let me explain what i think so. most of all experimenting with a five-day work week is making employee so tired. for example, when i was a employee. i was tired every day, so i wasn\'t able to focus on my work. but, when i was experimenting with a four-day work week, i was able to focus my work. also compaire to past, senior like my fathers age was experimenting with a six-day work week. but it\'s make it same performances when they worked fie days.','2026-03-27 17:22:03'),(38,1,1104,'FREE',2,NULL,NULL,'yes, i agree experimenting with a four-day work week. let me explain what i think so. most of all experimenting with a five-day work week is making employee so tired. for example, when i was a employee. i was tired every day, so i wasn\'t able to focus on my work. but, when i was experimenting with a four-day work week, i was able to focus my work. also compaire to past, senior like my fathers age was experimenting with a six-day work week. but it\'s make it same performances when they worked fie days.','2026-03-27 17:22:13'),(39,1,1105,'REAL',1,'/uploads/audio/user1_part3_q0_20260327_174609.webm',